	<title>Znanstveni zapis</title>
    
    <p>
    To enter numbers in scientific format use the <gui>×10y</gui> button (<keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>E</key></keyseq>).
    The <link xref="superscript">number mode</link> automatically changes to superscript.
    To enter 2×10¹⁰⁰, start by entering the mantissa (2):
    </p>
    <example>
    <p>2</p>
    </example>
    <p>Nato pritisnite gumb znanstvenega zapisa (ali pritisnite <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>E</key></keyseq>):</p>
    <example>
    <p>2×10</p>
    </example>
    <p>Nato vnesite eksponent (100):</p>
    <example>
    <p>2×10¹⁰⁰</p>
    </example>
    <p>Za prikaz rezultatov v znanstveno obliko spremenite <link xref="number-display">obliko rezultata</link>.</p>
